text: Nabiyow tama korosuk tama isin lac kee Buqrek sinnil carammosseenim Yalli siinil carammoyseemih siinih sumaaqita mara baahay keenik ixxic, tokkel usun dirab kee Almummah sumaaqiteenik, toysa Atu keenî luk masumaaqitin, Ni-Aayoota dirabboysa maray Akeerâ mano Nummaysewaah Nafsi fayxi makataatin, usun sinni Rabbit agleytit massoysan
